{"tid":1197957,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論：攻擊型收音機可行性","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:31:19.000Z","uid":50513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ba55a4638c228647ba4e1ce307bfb1f9a8a987","tid":1197957,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"如果有留意過dse新聞既巴打都應該對呢兩個terms唔陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幾年前讀緊細電果陣見到<br />\n就諗過下可行性<br />\n<br />\n理論上ee fyp都應該整到？<br />\n仲諗過整到拎住去考一次dse聆聽添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣仲諗過power夠大是咪可以一野隊死成場dse<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n初步概念：<br />\n<br />\n收音機 <br />\njammer+feedback circuit <br />\n做一個external plugin<br />\n<br />\n將jammer gen出黎既noise係接收方（收音機）<br />\n度當echo supress/cancel<br />\n但當中又有好多種tech 甚至有專用ic<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無細電大神可以幫手補充/指正返錯漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 純學術討論 果陣諗左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\nJammer <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=U8HKgoV5dAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU8HKgoV5dAQ&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GD8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=bb9e3bbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=U8HKgoV5dAQ</a><br />\n<br />\nEcho supression and cancellation <br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Echo_suppression_and_cancellation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEcho_suppression_and_cancellation&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GD8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=8980e552\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Echo_suppression_and_cancellation</a><br />\n<br />\necho cancellation 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eetimes.com/document.asp?doc_id=1277615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eetimes.com%2Fdocument.asp%3Fdoc_id%3D1277615&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GD8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=5ac25381\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eetimes.com/document.asp?doc_id=1277615</a><br />\n<br />\nSimple radio circuit<br />\n<a href=\"https://electronicsforu.com/electronics-projects/simple-fm-receiver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectronicsforu.com%2Felectronics-projects%2Fsimple-fm-receiver&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GD8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=68821179\" target=\"_blank\">https://electronicsforu.com/electronics-projects/simple-fm-receiver</a>"},{"pid":"0057c61b7ff00dba12ea1266cbe20b220482414d","tid":1197957,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"範圍限制?"},{"pid":"ec6b9cbe36075d5571d867d05be3f7a9c31c33b2","tid":1197957,"uid":50513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0057c61b7ff00dba12ea1266cbe20b220482414d","tid":1197957,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"範圍限制?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"理論上應該係跟jammer個power<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4669023e6c1124adc0e044aba9c667c546b6ea","tid":1197957,"uid":51672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"雖然唔識但支持"},{"pid":"a57ed1a9c6986b88f609127226f314f1bf11168c","tid":1197957,"uid":131757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"係<span style=\"color: red;\">全攻</span>型收音機阿!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5274172725953a53b42ced3c30baee953d913a8a","tid":1197957,"uid":98313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:07:10.000Z","m